    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> You are about to roll initiative in an encounter in which your asset is one of your opponents.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You read the demeanor, body language, and instinctive tics of your asset as easily as you read a comm unit, allowing you to react a moment before those around you and gain an edge in the coming battle. You gain a +1 circumstance bonus to your initiative roll, and you can immediately do one of the following: Interact to draw a weapon, Step, or Stride.</p>"
